'''耶胡迪爾''' ([[希伯來語|希伯來語]]：{{Hebrew|'''יהודיאל'''}}，[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|'''Jegudiel'''}} 或 {{lang|en|'''Jehudiel'''}}；東正教譯'''耶谷迪伊爾'''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.crkvenikalendar.com/datumcn-2015-11-21 |title=+++ 紀念天軍之統帥彌哈伊爾總領天使及其餘天軍神將 |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2015-11-21 |website=crkvenikalendar.com |access-date=2019-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212193343/https://www.crkvenikalendar.com/datumcn-2015-11-21 |archive-date=2017-12-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>)，名字意為「神之讚美」，是[[正教會|東正教會]]和[[東儀天主教會|東儀天主教會]]傳統中的七大[[天使長|天使長]]之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.orthodox.cn/prologue/March26.htm |title=Hymn of Praise: The Archangels |access-date=2016-01-29 |archive-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207030940/http://www.orthodox.cn/prologue/March26.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 形像 ==
祂在[[聖像畫|聖像]]中被描繪為手持[[皇冠|皇冠]]和帶有三根鞭條的[[鞭|鞭子]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.holy-transfiguration.org/library_en/ang_powers.html |title=The Rational Heavenly Powers |access-date=2016-01-29 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111170210/http://www.holy-transfiguration.org/library_en/ang_powers.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>皇冠象徵[[基督教的神|上帝]]給予義人的獎賞，鞭子象徵對罪人的懲罰。[[正教會|東正教]]對祂的傳統表現形式是站立之像，右手持[[皇冠|皇冠]]，左手持[[權杖|權杖]]。

== 主保 ==
耶胡迪爾是那些努力工作之人的[[主保聖人|守護聖者]]，祂手持之皇冠即象徵著對那些成功的[[靈性|靈性]]勞作者的獎勵。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.holy-transfiguration.org/library_en/ang_heavhost.html |title=The heavenly host and our modern life |accessdate=2016-01-29 |archive-date=2019-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827125831/http://www.holy-transfiguration.org/library_en/ang_heavhost.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 禱文 ==
作為努力工作和領導地位的[[主保聖人|守護聖者]]而獻予耶胡迪爾的禱文：
{{translateH}}
{{lang|en|Saint Jegudiel the Archangel, angel of praise to God, pray for us, that in every act, in every job, in every work, and in every labor we may constantly carry out the will of the Lord gladly and in praise for all He has given us.  Amen.}}
{{translateF}}

作為神之慈悲的[[主保聖人|守護聖者]]而獻予耶胡迪爾的禱文：
{{translateH}}
{{lang|en|O merciful Archangel, St. Jhudiel, dispenser of God's eternal and abundant Mercy. Because of our sinfulness, we do not deserve God's forgiveness. Yet, He continually grants us forbearance freely and lovingly. Help us in our determination to overcome our sinful habits and be truly sorry for them. Bring each one of us to true conversion of heart. That we may experience  the joy of reconciliation which it brings, without which neither we, as individuals, nor the whole world can know true peace. You who continually intercede for us, listen to our prayers. Present to God our Father all these petitions.  Through Jesus Christ our Lord, together with the Holy Spirit forever and ever. Amen.}}
{{translateF}}

